snippet.title: Rooted - Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Rooted is a post-apocalyptic survival game built in Unreal Engine 5, and a gameplay trailer debuted during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022 featured building, exploring and combat. Rooted is coming soon.
